          Someone Else  <a role="button" class="btn btn-primary collapsed" data-toggle="collapse"  data-target="#share-form" ><span title="Share this profile"  class="fa fa-share-alt"  aria-hidden="true" ></span></a>
        </h2>
        <div class="collapse " id="share-form" >
